HEADWORD: Shindy
<hw>Shin"dy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Shindies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Etymol. uncertain; cf.
<er>Shinney</er>, <er>Shinty</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An uproar or
